ast.name: ninja game
ast.comment: Simple game showing animation and touch input

body.text: Creates a picture of a target (alternation of rings red and foreground color)
Pick random position on board and animate target to oscillate around it. Assumes there already is a spring between anchor and target.
Shoot 5 ninja stars and try to hit a target. Target moves to new position once it is hit.

thenBody.text: repositions the target at a random new position
